    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>\"Don't you dare disrespect the Uchiha Clan\"</em></p><h5 id=\"benefit\">Benefit</h5><p>You have a lot of pride in yourself, due to how good you are. Twice per day you can add a d8 to any d20 roll.</p><h5 id=\"negative\">Negative</h5><p>You hate to have your ego hurt. If after you have added the d8 to the d20 roll you still fail, you take 1d10 psychic damage. This damage cannot be lowered in any way.</p>",
